<div class="container-fluid">
	<h2>開始你的書卷讀經</h2>
  <p>
  	您可以直接選擇要讀的<a href="#book_select">聖經書卷</a>，
  	如果您不知道從那卷書開始，請參考下面的建議。
  </p>
</div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row-fluid">

          <div class="span2">
            <p>
            </p>
            <p>
            </p>
            <img data-src="holder.js/100x100" class="img-rounded" alt="100x100" style="width: 120px; height: 120px;" src="/light 1.jpg">
          </div>

            <h3>
              直接選擇你想閲讀的聖經書卷:
            </h3>
       
          <div class="span10">

            <table class="table table-hover" width="560" >

              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th width="100" scope="col">書卷分類</th>
                  <th width="460" scope="col">書卷名稱</th>
                </tr>

                <% @book_series_1.collections.each do |collection| %>

                  <tr>
                    <td>
                    <!--
                    <% if collection.id < 6 %><span class="badge badge-warning">
                        <% else %><span class="badge badge-info"><% end %>
                      <%= collection.id %></span> 
                    -->
                      <% if collection.id < 6 %><span class="badge badge-warning">舊約</span>
                      <% else %><span class="badge badge-info">新約</span>
                      <% end %>
                       
                      <%= link_to collection.title, book_series_collection_url(@book_series_1, collection) %>
                    </td>
                    <td>|
                      <% collection.books.each do |book| %>
                        <%= link_to book.title, book_series_collection_book_url(@book_series_1, collection, book) %> |
                      <% end %>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                <% end %>
                <tr>
                  <td></td>
                  <td></td>
                </tr>

              </tbody>
            </table>

           </div>
         </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row-fluid">

          <div class="span2">
            <p>
            </p>
            <p>
            </p>
            <img data-src="holder.js/100x100" class="img-rounded" alt="100x100" style="width: 120px; height: 120px;" src="/light 3.jpg">
          </div>

          <h3>
            設定你的書卷讀經計劃：
          </h3>

          <div class="span10">
            <p>
              讀聖經最重要的就是按著您的需要和聖經基礎，選擇合適的書卷，並持之以恆讀完。maxBibleReader願意幫助你完成每一卷書，並且享受其中。
            </p>
            <p>
            <span class="badge badge-important">1</span> 設定
            </p>

            <%= render 'plan_form' %>

          </div>

        </div>
      </div>





